actions.message:
`!help <page>` - Used to view help documents.
Example Usage: _!help general_

`!kick {@username} {Reason}` - Kicks a user from the server.

`!ban {@username} {Reason}` - Bans a user from the server.

`!userid {@username}` - Checks userid to a specific user.

`!ban {@username} {Reason}` - Bans a user from the server.

`!purge {how many messages}` - Deleting chat, `!purge` clear all messages.

`!staffappstatus {open/closed}` - Sets the status of staff application.

`!warn {@username} {Reason}` - Gives the user a warning.

`!clearwarnings {@username}` - **NOT WORKING YET**

`!mute {@username} {minutes} {Reason}` - **IMPORTANT**, you need to make a role called "Muted"

`!mutesetup {#yourchannel}` - Replace #yourchannel with a text-channel, e.g ``#mute-log``
